simnibs.write_msh¶

simnibs.write_msh(msh, file_name=None, mode='binary')¶

Writes a gmsh ‘msh’ file

Parameters

  • msh (simnibs.msh.Msh) – Mesh structure

  • file_name (str (optional)) – Name of file to be writte. Default: msh.fn

  • mode ('binary' or 'ascii':) – The mode in which the file should be read
